description: Cat Fact will tell you over 100 interesting things about cats. This skill will give you a random cat fact when called. Now you can learn about cats for fun by simply asking, "Ask Cat Fact for a fact."
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Cat Fact to tell me a cat fact.
Alexa, tell Cat Fact to give me a fact.
name: Cat Fact
shortDescription: Learn about cats with the Cat Fact skill
